---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'ms';
const post = {
  title: 'Baru vs Terpakai - Optimalan Budget 2026',
  slug: 'baru-vs-terpakai-optimalan-budget-2026',
  excerpt: 'Baru vs terpakai peralatan? Panduan optimalan budget 2026. Peralatan terpakai 40-60% lebih murah dengan 0% deposit. Bank tak biayai >5 tahun. Ing Heng biayai sehingga 10 tahun.',
  date: '2026-01-01',
  author: 'Pasukan Ing Heng Credit',
  readTime: 4,
  category: 'Pembiayaan Peralatan',
  image: '/images/blog/excavator-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['baru vs terpakai', 'peralatan terpakai', 'optimalan budget', 'pembiayaan peralatan lama', '0% deposit'];
const breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Utama', href: '/ms' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/ms/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/ms/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Pembiayaan Peralatan</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('ms-MY', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min bacaan</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Baru vs Terpakai - Pilihan Bijak</h2>

      <p>Peralatan baharu menawarkan warranty dan teknologi terkini. Tetapi harga tinggi. Peralatan terpakai lebih jimat, serendah 40% harga baharu.</p>

      <p>Pilihan antara baharu dan terpakai bergantung kepada budget dan keperluan perniagaan anda.</p>

      <h2>Peralatan Baharu - Kelebihan & Kekurangan</h2>

      <p>Peralatan baharu mempunyai kelebihan:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Warranty:</strong> Perlindungan penuh</li>
        <li><strong>Teknologi:</strong> Terkini, canggih</li>
        <li><strong>Effisiensi:</strong> Bahan api jimat</li>
        <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> Kurang masalah</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Tetapi harga tinggi - 2-3x lebih mahal dari terpakai.</p>

      <h2>Peralatan Terpakai - Jimat & Praktikal</h2>

      <p>Peralatan terpakai menawarkan nilai jimat:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Harga:</strong> 40-60% lebih murah</li>
        <li><strong>Proven:</strong> Sudah tested</li>
        <li><strong>Availability:</strong> Sedia ada</li>
        <li><strong>Depresiasi:</strong> Kurang loss</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Tetapi bank tak suka pembiayaan peralatan >5 tahun.</p>

      <h2>Jadual Perbandingan</h2>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background: #2D1810; color: white;">
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left;">Ciri-ciri</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">Bank (Baru)</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">Bank (Terpakai)</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">Ing Heng</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Deposit</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">10-20%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">10-20%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;"><strong>0%</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f9fafb;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Had Umur</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">5 tahun</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; color: #dc2626;">Biasa ditolak</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;"><strong>Tiada had</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Pembiayaan</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">90%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; color: #dc2626;">Sukar</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;"><strong>100%</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Contoh Sebenar - Budget Optimization</h2>

      <p><strong>Pilihan:</strong> Eskavator Komatsu</p>

      <p><strong>Baharu:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Harga: RM150,000</li>
        <li>Deposit (Bank 10%): RM15,000</li>
        <li>Pinjaman: RM135,000</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Terpakai (7 tahun):</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Harga: RM45,000 (70% jimat!)</li>
        <li>Deposit (Bank): Biasa ditolak</li>
        <li>Deposit (Ing Heng): <strong>RM0</strong></li>
        <li>Pinjaman: <strong>RM45,000</strong></li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Jimat:</strong> RM105,000 + RM15,000 deposit = RM120,000!</p>

      <h2>Harga Peralatan Terpakai</h2>

      <p>Peralatan terpakai yang kami biayai:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Komatsu terpakai:</strong> Dari RM34,000</li>
        <li><strong>CAT terpakai:</strong> Dari RM50,000</li>
        <li><strong>Forklift terpakai:</strong> Dari RM15,000</li>
        <li><strong>Lori terpakai:</strong> Dari RM25,000</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Bila Pilih Terpakai?</h2>

      <p>Pilih terpakai jika:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Budget ketat:</strong> Jimat besar</li>
        <li><strong>Startup:</strong> Modal terhad</li>
        <li><strong>Penggunaan biasa:</strong> Tak perlukan high-tech</li>
        <li><strong>ROI cepat:</strong> Nak balik modal cepat</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Hubungi Kami</h2>

      <p>Baru atau terpakai? Kami boleh biayai kedua-duanya dengan 0% deposit. Hubungi kami hari ini.</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Pembiayaan Baru & Terpakai - 0% Deposit</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Dapatkan kelulusan dalam 24-48 jam. WhatsApp kami untuk konsultasi percuma.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Hubungi:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Telefon)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Dapatkan Pembiayaan Peralatan" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  strong {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #D4A574;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
